 ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Most of all , have fun with it<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>Anyone in the guild (except officers) will create a lvl 1 Troll. From the zone to da swamp in South Ro, we will have a race to Highpass. It would go S Ro, Oasis, N Ro, EC, WC, to the zone to Highpass. But speed will not be the only thing you need to win!<br><br>There will be a specified officer in each zone you pass through. Each Troll must hail this officer as they pass through. The officers must be outside in plain view and cannot go invis or hide. I personally will be in Kithicor  This way, the person with the fastest LOADING times won't neccesarily win.<br><br>Now this sounds tough. Won't it be dangerous?&quot; Well I say to you, YES it will be dangerous! That will be all the fun to it! And even more, every Troll MUST turn in the book to the priest of discord! This way, we will have up to 40 naked Trolls in one brutal, backstabbing, race to the finish! The strongest will survive!<br><br>I also add, it would be best and strongly suggested for members creating a lvl 1 troll to use the first 3-4 letters of there main chars name , so as it is easy to identify them in guildsay and makes it that much more personal and fun!!!<br>These trolls will be invited to guild by officers in the starting zone...this will keep us all in the loop of the trechorous run they will endeavor *EG*<br>Have fun with it!!<br>We also have some former guild memebers that wish to participate in this event!!<br>Lixandrya Lolovivi<br>40th Season Paladin <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fjestapowa12244frm3.showPrevMessage?topicID=2.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub98.ezboard.com/fjestapowa12244frm